dct_title_s: International Travel Maps, Shanghai & China southeast / edited by Yusuke Ujimaya, Mark Ramsay, Edgar Mantashyan, Dung Nguyen,  Phuong Vu, TRan Dinh Cung ; Lan Joyce, editor in chief.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights on map of China southeast. Shows roads, subway stations, railways, and various tourist attractions. Title from panel. Includes indexes and tourist notes. Ancillary map: Shanghai region. Scale1:210,000. On alternate panel: Shanghai Metro.
